rgamer.com/dnd/races\">DnD races guide</a>\n\t\t\t", "id": 1327572, "language": "en-US", "link": "https://www.wargamer.com/dnd/magic-items", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 86, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 384, "source_url": "https://www.wargamer.com/mainrss.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://www.wargamer.com/wp-content/sites/wargamer/2024/05/dnd-magic-items-potions.jpg", "title": "20 shiny new DnD magic items from the 2024 DM\u2019s Guide", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-15T13:08:22.890895+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://www.wargamer.com/wp-content/sites/wargamer/2024/10/dnd-dms-guide-monster-manual-hints.jpg\" class=\"webfeedsFeaturedVisual\" alt=\"DnD&#8217;s new DM&#8217;s Guide is stuffed with spoilers for the 2025 Monster Manual\" title=\"DnD&#8217;s new DM&#8217;s Guide is stuffed with spoilers for the 2025 Monster Manual\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>We\u2019ve had an early glimpse of <b>DnD</b>\u2019s 2024 Dungeon Master\u2019s Guide, and it\u2019s filled with hints about what\u2019s coming in the new Monster Manual. Yes, it\u2019s <i>also</i> filled with useful DMing advice, magic items, and optional rules. But weaved in with those ideas are plenty of details about how enemies will change in the new \u2018edition-ish\u2019 of Dungeons and Dragons.</p>\n \t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\tContinue reading <a href=\"https://www.wargamer.com/dnd/dms-guide-monster-manual-hints\">DnD&#8217;s new DM&#8217;s Guide is stuffed with spoilers for the 2025 Monster Manual</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\tMORE FROM WARGAMER: <a href=\"https://www.warga", "id": 1327571, "language": "en-US", "link": "https://www.wargamer.com/dnd/dms-guide-monster-manual-hints", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 86, "pag