ent/sites/wargamer/2024/10/dnd-celeb-consultants-dms-guide-2.jpg", "title": "Dungeons and Dragons\u2019 new DM Guide has some surprise celeb consultants", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-15T13:08:16.031058+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://www.wargamer.com/wp-content/sites/wargamer/2024/10/dnd-2024-dungeon-masters-guide-review-book-1.jpg\" class=\"webfeedsFeaturedVisual\" alt=\"DnD 2024 Dungeon Master\u2019s Guide review - fun, but not flaw-free\" title=\"DnD 2024 Dungeon Master\u2019s Guide review - fun, but not flaw-free\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>If you\u2019re here, it\u2019s because you\u2019re seeking out a <b>DnD 2024 Dungeon Master\u2019s Guide review</b>. I\u2019ve spent an extensive number of hours studying Wizards of the Coast\u2019s newest rulebook (thank you to the publisher for providing a copy), so I can explain in detail where it peaks and troughs. But first, let\u2019s get a few simple questions out of the way.</p>\n \t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\tContinue reading <a href=\"https://www.wargamer.com/dnd/2024-dungeon-masters-guide-review\">DnD 2024 Dungeon Master\u2019s Guide review - fun, but not flaw-free</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\tMORE FROM WARGAMER: <a href=\"https://www.wargamer.com/dnd/2024-players-handbook-review\">DnD 2024 Player's Handbook ", "id": 1327569, "language": "en-US", "link": "https://www.wargamer.com/dnd/2024-dungeon-masters-guide-review", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 86, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 384, "source_url": "https://www.wargamer.com/mainrss.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://www.wargamer.com/wp-content/sites/wargamer/2024/10/dnd-2024-dungeon-masters-guide-review-book-1.jpg", "title": "DnD 2024 Dungeon Master\u2019s Guide review - fun, but not flaw-free", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-15T13:08:13.597285+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://www.wargamer.com/wp-content/sites/wargamer/2024/10/dnd-safety-tools-dms-guide.jpg\" class=\"webfeedsFeaturedVisual\" alt=\"DnD&#8217;s new Dungeon Master&#8217;s Guide apes other RPGs without giving due credit\" title=\"DnD&#8217;s new Dungeon Master&#8217;s Guide apes other RPGs without giving due credit\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><b>Dungeons and Dragons</b>\u2019 Dungeon Master Guide finally features safety tools. These additional rules help ensure everyone at the table is having fun, and other RPGs made them a staple of play long before D&amp;D joined the crowd. After such tools were featured in less essential 5e supplements, I\u2019m glad to see the 2024 DM\u2019s Guide follow this industry trend and add safety tools to its core rules. However, it disappoints me that D&amp;D hasn\u2019t given due credit to the creators of these consent tools.</p>\n \t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\tContinue reading <a href=\"https://www.wargamer.com/dnd/safety-tools-dms-guide\">DnD&#8217;s new Dungeon Mas", "id": 1327568, "language": "en-US", "link": "https://www.wargamer.com/dnd/safety-tools-dms-guide", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 86, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 384, "source_url": "https://www.wargamer.com/mainrss.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://www.wargamer.com/wp-content/sites/wargamer/2024/10/dnd-safety-tools-dms-guide.jpg", "title": "DnD\u2019s new Dungeon Master\u2019s Guide apes other RPGs without giving due credit", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-15T12:02:10.798336+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://www.wargamer